es for a commutative, contractive operator pair, extending\nresults of Sz.-Nagy--Foias for the single-operator case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Sep 2018 21:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Sep 2018 02:29:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-01"}
