tions between somatic mutations and cancers. The discovered genes and\npathways associated with each cancer type can lead to biological insights. The\nproposed method can be adapted to other studies for disease classification and\npathway discovery.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Sep 2018 13:22:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 19:56:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
